data.description: Home being sold AS-IS. This is an investor or DIYers dream! Ready for your own personal touch. Vaulted ceiling in the living room gives a wonderful open feeling. Eat-in kitchen includes plentiful storage including a walk-in pantry and a bonus second pantry. The double oven is perfect for entertaining and holidays. Quartz countertops in primary bathroom. Wood-look tile recently installed in primary and secondary bedroom, but the project needs to be completed. Foundation/drainage repairs needed. Primary bedroom took on water during the tax day floods. New hot water heater 2023, new roof 2021. Home is eligible for a conventional renovation loan. Please ask agent for more information!
